data.description: MLS#273109 $5,000 Buyers Credit! Step into warmth and comfort with this meticulously maintained 2006-built home nestled in a friendly neighborhood. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms spread over 1734 square feet, this residence offers an inviting atmosphere that welcomes you from the moment you enter. The neighborhood has a real sense of community you’ll experience while enjoying peaceful walks in the serene surroundings.  Bask in the abundant natural light that fills the open floor plan featuring vaulted ceilings and generously spacious rooms. The heart of this home extends outdoors, where you'll find a delightful back patio – a perfect spot to relax in the shade or host brunches with loved ones. Step into the backyard adorned with 2 peach trees and 2 pear trees, generously bearing fruits, creating a picturesque setting.  The 6-foot fence provides both privacy and security, making the backyard an ideal haven for pets to roam freely. Whether you're enjoying the tranquility of your surroundings or taking advantage of the flourishing greenery, this residence embodies the essence of a welcoming home in a community that values togetherness and peaceful living. Contact your favorite Realtor today for your private showing!
